document_data.mainbody:
age Street was a small road that was located in the city of Waterdeep.
Cage Street was located in Waterdeeps Castle Ward. It originated on the southern end of the Street of Silver, branching west through a neighborhood of buildings to end where it merged with Shadow Alley. Mulgomirs Way intersected Cage Street close to where it branched from the Street of Silver.
* The Dragons Head tavern
